race.comment: DISNEY CASTLE (3) has been racing well, winning two back then running on hard to just miss latest. Peaks and ready for the longer trip now. HEREDITARY (7) continues to race very well and regular rider Dolan aboard again. Drawn to feature in the finish, AMERICAN PHIREBALL (8) wound up strongly to just miss last time. Loves it here and looks hard to hold out again. GALANO (1) turned in an average effort last start when sixth and beaten 7 lengths over 1800m at Eagle Farm. Better than last start and does tend to run best in these conditions. Has the claim offsetting the big weight and definitely worth another chance.
